quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,24,"Aey Nabi, Ibrahim ke muazzaz mehmano ki hiqayat bhi tumhein pahunchi hai"
  51,25,Jab woh uske haan (yahan) aaye to kaha aapko salaam hai. Usne kaha “ aap logon ko bhi salaam hai kuch na-aashna se log hain”
  51,26,"Phir woh chupke se apne ghar walon ke paas gaya, aur ek mota taaza bachda (calf) laa kar"
  51,27,Mehmanon ke aage pesh kiya. Usne kaha aap hazraat khate nahin
  51,28,"Phir woh apne dil mein unse dara. Unhon ne kaha dariye nahin, aur usey ek zee-ilm ladke ki paidaish ka mushda (good news/basharat) sunaya"
  51,29,"Yeh sunkar uski biwi cheekhti hui aage badhi aur usne apna mooh peeth liya aur kehne lagi, “boodhi baanj”"
  51,30,Unhon ne kaha “yahi kuch farmaya hai tere Rubb ne. Woh hakeem hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai
  51,31,"Ibrahim ne kaha “aey farstaadgaan-e-ilaahi (envoys), kya mohim aapko dar-pesh hai"
  51,32,Unhon ne kaha “hum ek mujrim qaum ki taraf bheje gaye hain
  51,33,Taa-ke uspar paki hui mitti ke patthar (clay-stones) barsa de
  51,34,Jo aapke Rubb ke haan hadd se guzar jane walon ke liye nishan zada hain”
  51,35,Phir humne un sab logon ko nikal liya jo us basti mein momin thay
  51,36,Aur wahan humne ek ghar ke siwa musalmano ka koi ghar na paya
  51,37,Uske baad humne wahan bas ek nishani un logon ke liye chodh di jo dardnaak azaab se darte hon
  51,38,Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Moosa ke qissey mein jab humne usey sareeh sanad (clear authority) ke saath Firoun ke paas bheja
  51,39,To woh apne bal-bootay par akad gaya aur bola yeh jaadugar hai ya majnoon(deewana) hai
  51,40,Aakhir-e-kaar humne usey aur uske lashkaron ko pakda aur sabko samandar mein phenk diya aur woh malamat zadah hokar reh gaya
  51,41,"Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Aad (people of Aad) mein, jabke humne unpar ek aisi hi bay-khair(devastating) hawa bhej di"
  51,42,Ke jis cheez par bhi woh guzar gayi usey boseeda (rotten) karke rakh diya
  51,43,"Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Samood mein, jab unse kaha gaya tha ke ek khaas waqt tak mazey karlo"
  51,44,Magar is tambeeh(warning) par bhi unhon ne apne Rubb ke hukum se sartabi (brazenly disobey) ki. Aakhir-e-kar unke dekhte dekhte ek achanak toot padne waley azaab ne unko aa liya
  51,45,Phir na unmein uthne ki sakat thi aur na woh apna bachao kar sakte thay
  51,46,Aur in sabse pehle humne Nooh ki qaum ko halaak kiya kyunke woh fasiq (wicked) log thay